{
  "design_notes": "The medium chart focuses on translating the track's driving energy into comfortably flowing 4th and 8th-note patterns. In S0, we introduce gentle steps on the dominant beats. S1 opens up the drop with basic zigzag motions and accent jumps on downbeats. S2 acts as a steady physical build, incorporating light streams. The massive body of S3 uses a series of well-spaced holds that align with the synth sustains, testing the player's limb coordination while maintaining crossovers at a light level. Pruned downbeats and syncopations ensure we remain strictly within the 5.0 NPS medium difficulty threshold. S4 provides a slow cooldown, transitioning into quiet, spaced taps to guide the player safely to the end of the song.",
